# Google Gemini API Configuration
# Get your FREE API key at: https://makersuite.google.com/app/apikey

# Your Gemini API Key (starts with "AI...")
VITE_GEMINI_API_KEY=AIza...your-api-key-here

# Optional: Backend API Proxy URL (recommended for production security)
# Example: https://your-backend-api.com
VITE_API_PROXY=

# ==========================================
# HOW TO GET YOUR GEMINI API KEY (FREE):
# ==========================================
# 1. Go to: https://makersuite.google.com/app/apikey
# 2. Sign in with your Google account
# 3. Click "Get API Key" or "Create API Key"
# 4. Copy the API key (starts with "AIza...")
# 5. Paste it above in VITE_GEMINI_API_KEY=
# 6. Save this file as ".env" (remove .example)
# 7. Restart your dev server: npm run dev
#
# IMPORTANT SECURITY NOTES:
# - Never commit .env to Git (it's in .gitignore)
# - For production, use a backend proxy to hide the API key
# - Free tier includes generous usage limits
# - Gemini Pro is completely FREE (no credit card required!)
